15#ifndef ISCCFG_LOG_H
16#define ISCCFG_LOG_H 1
17
18/*! \file isccfg/log.h */
19
20#include <isc/lang.h>
21#include <isc/log.h>
22
23LIBISCCFG_EXTERNAL_DATA extern isc_logcategory_t cfg_categories[];
24LIBISCCFG_EXTERNAL_DATA extern isc_logmodule_t cfg_modules[];
25
26#define CFG_LOGCATEGORY_CONFIG (&cfg_categories[0])
27
28#define CFG_LOGMODULE_PARSER (&cfg_modules[0])
29
30ISC_LANG_BEGINDECLS
31
32void
33cfg_log_init(isc_log_t *lctx);
34/*%<
35 * Make the libisccfg categories and modules available for use with the
36 * ISC logging library.
37 *
38 * Requires:
39 *\li lctx is a valid logging context.
40 *
41 *\li cfg_log_init() is called only once.
42 *
43 * Ensures:
44 * \li The categories and modules defined above are available for
45 * use by isc_log_usechannnel() and isc_log_write().
46 */
47
48ISC_LANG_ENDDECLS
49
50#endif /* ISCCFG_LOG_H */
